untie 死全家 <br />\n再見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e1509102dad56402e8ec52810d41bbd28bdda7","tid":16957,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35dc2d8f6f9ee1a83973ff0248918afd5244c7c","tid":16957,"uid":49302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:46:28.000Z","msg":"跪佢老母啦<br />\n<br />\n叫佢直播含撚我就考慮下番去......一分鐘咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1156f4478c5dee916e7e62758a197c6ea24aee9a","tid":16957,"uid":9281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:50:06.000Z","msg":"早洩直播食屎我考慮下返高登一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5eac7877d275c5a1766a02b9e24f04f26f87d13","tid":16957,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:51:27.000Z","msg":"返去俾人bam咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw唔好再貼高登野 唔想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23883949d9278d4385b379ec2fe1d2f5f900bc1c","tid":16957,"uid":41552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早洩直播食屎我考慮下返高登一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢食唔食屎早唔早泄都唔關我地事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a03c1a26a455dd5e16b44e388f27e513d1a2c21","tid":16957,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:09:41.000Z","msg":"大勢已去先話著手研究app改善m版<br />\nSmartphone興到而家有成7年比你啊大哥 做it狗做到話唔知會員用咩platform上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif